{"tid":2225293,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"年尾前坐九巴龍運滿200蚊 送一盒30個口罩","createTime":"2020-10-01T08:02:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-12T14:54:53.000Z","uid":178875,"like":11,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"1ee677fcdf2d643427644f8f52c729b6192d603c","tid":2225293,"uid":178875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T08:02:18.000Z","msg":"九巴龍運 FUN分賞 搭巴士賺積分換禮品<br />\n九巴及龍運推出全新獎賞計劃「FUN分賞」，乘客只需於App1933登記，便可邊搭巴士邊賺積分，換取既實用又精美的禮品，搭得越多獎賞越多。<br />\n<br />\n先登記後儲分　搭得多賺得多<br />\n<br />\n10月1日至12月31日期間，乘客在App1933以八達通號碼登記「九巴龍運 FUN分賞」，便可立即參與獎賞計劃，用已先登記的八達通卡乘搭任何九巴或龍運營運的巴士班次*，每繳付車資$0.1即可賺取0.1分。賺取的積分可換取精品，第一階段推出九巴三層外科成人口罩一盒 (30個)，只須400分便可免費換領。在推廣期內，首次登記更即送200積分。九巴及龍運禮品會陸續推出，保證驚喜源源不絕。<br />\n<br />\n積分計算以實際繳付的車費為準，使用九巴月票的車程並不適用。乘客亦可於App1933查閱已登記八達通的積分。<br />\n<br />\n*非九巴及龍運營運之聯營線班次，以及K12、K14、K17及K18線，均不包括「FUN分賞」計劃內。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.kmb.hk/tc/news/press/archives/news202009303711.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.kmb.hk%2Ftc%2Fnews%2Fpress%2Farchives%2Fnews202009303711.html&d=2MheXYw%2FBwPqfvV%2BE34w16nyrFheAedOz%2Bkyyi3ikZI%3D&h=2cbabba0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.kmb.hk/tc/news/press/archives/news202009303711.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/e5Vg5Qa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fe5Vg5Qa.jpg&h=1a8dcb9b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6a5db51d7c205e6fba5f119eb0f7ff26b06a9120","tid":2225293,"uid":127929,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T08:03:52.000Z","msg":"有用po!推!"},{"pid":"33379227563cbff7894c7f066252b38aec4c47c2","tid":2225293,"uid":178875,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T08:08:47.000Z","msg":"大西北朋友<br />\n用完一張再用另一張<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bda9ddbc5c68162a130ba3a25a3df4b2f0aad2ef","tid":2225293,"uid":178875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T08:18:58.000Z","msg":"